# Trims the build context for images built from the repository root (the
# install-test image - see dev/docker/install-test/Dockerfile). The dev-tools
# image builds from its own sub-folder context and is unaffected.
#
# That Dockerfile only COPYs provision.sh and the tool manifests; everything
# else is bind-mounted at run time, so the heavy, build-irrelevant trees are
# dropped here to keep the context transfer fast.
.git
var
